<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1182: Rear End Door / Trunk Lid Request Switch Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Rear end door request switch signal voltage is lower than specified value for specified time.
</ptxt>
</entry>
